# Testing

## Stack

- Mocha + Chai; Sinon when stubbing is needed
- File naming: `<module>.spec.js` alongside or under `test/`
- Babel register required — use ES6 `import` like existing specs

## Practices

- Test behavior, not implementation details
- Integration tests: pipe through `XLSXTransformStream`, unzip with `unzipper`, compare file buffers to `test/test.xlsx`
- Use `Readable` in `objectMode` with row arrays as input chunks
- Dev dependencies in tests are allowed (`import/no-extraneous-dependencies` override)

## Commands

```bash
npm test        # build + run all specs
npm run test-cov  # optional coverage
```

Add or update specs when changing stream behavior, cell types, or XML output.
